%p
.row
  .small-12.large-8.small-centered.large-centered.column.whitewash

    %p
    .div
      %h5.blue

        %p
        Hi! I'd love to test 
        #{@recipe.name}! 

        %p
        Here's a little about me:
        %p
      %h5.darkgrey        
        =@tester.tester_bio 
      %h5.blue
        %p
        Thanks!
        %br
        =@tester.name

      %p
      %hr
    .upper
      %a.button{:href=>"/recipes/approved?id="+@recipe.id.to_s+"&tester="+@tester.id.to_s}
        Sweet. Approve them for this recipe.
      %p
      %a.button.warning{:href=>"/recipes/rejected?id="+@recipe.id.to_s+"&tester="+@tester.id.to_s}
        Nah, not for this recipe. 

      %p
      %a.button.success{:href=>"/users/whitelist?tester="+@tester.id.to_s}
        =@tester.name
        is awesome. Auto-Approve for any of my recipes!
      %p
      %a.button.alert{:href=>"/users/blacklist?tester="+@tester.id.to_s}
        I'd rather not have this person testing. Please hide further requests.

